          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is now third year of my daughter in Vibgyor Roots and Rise. I wud like to say we have had wonderful experience so far coz I have seen the way my daughter is getting better day by day in studies, SPA, responsibilities etc. Throughout the year there are multiple activities like PTM, Culminating, SPA, Annual Sports, Viva, Summer camp and .... Etc\nShall like to Thank the efforts put by all the teachers and Sir. Also thanking Class V  teacher Anamika Ma'am, Manish Sir, Madhuri Ma'am.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
