            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Best school in our area .\nNeed to improve communication in management and parents .\nTeachers are amazing . 😍\nFor 2 grade we will like to see another next year to Rajashri and Khooshboo mam , and\nFor 6th grade Swati and Anamika mam as the same .",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "VIBGYOR ROOTS &amp; RISE - Fursungi"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Rajashree Chavan"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-31",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "If you want to take admission here please be sure first. Bcoz once you took admission the administration will not support you in cancelation process also whatever amount you paid will get lost.\n\nI took my daughters admission and within a month due to job transfer I need to cancel it. The school was not started yet still the management is not able to refund the amount.\n\nWhile taking the admission they behave very nicely and ready to help you but once you pay the amount they don't care about anything. They just want money.\n\nDon't take admission here.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "VIBGYOR ROOTS &amp; RISE - Fursungi"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sangram Shinde"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-30",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Do not take admissions here. And by mistake if you take don't/never pay full amount. Don't go for any offer's for saving some amount....You will be in policy traps , if you want to cancel or take admission to different schools you will lose your money. At least They proved with me that they are only collection centre. Very disappointing misguiding parents about cancelation and fee refund. Policies are written only to empty your pocket. I took admission and paid first installment amount in feb.23 during admission itself. due to my personal reasons i have to cancel admission of my daughter for Jr. Kg. I sent cancellation request in Month March 23, i thought my proactiveness will help school to backfill this position immediately. As Yet, School is to be started in June 23. I asked to cancel admission and refund amount. I said it is absolutely fine to debit any inconveniences fees. But As per policy they can't refund any amount at any circumstances the fees which i paid!\n\nRequest to Vibgyor Top Management, stop fooling the parents. Review your policies.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        }
      ]
